Michael Busteed salutes during his remarks during a ceremony to honor the memory of Breonna Moffett, Thursday, Feb. 1, 2024, at Windsor Forest High School in Savannah. Moffitt joined the Army Reserve in 2019, after graduating from high school. She was among three Georgia soldiers killed in a Jordan drone attack. (AJC Photo/Stephen B.
